I put in one of the "short shift" kits for a beetle. They are the same size 
and bolt right in. My shifter stops about 4 or 5 inches from the dash board 
now. It does make a little hump in the rubber mat though.

Just don't get the el-cheapo $4 ones. They crack and break too easily.

